<p>Reports information sent by E. Schulte [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">12254</hi>] on the colours of the male <hi rend="italic">Diadema bolina</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Discusses extent to which consciousness came into play in the origin of certain instincts, including sexual display.</p>
